      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty! Honestly, it's in such incredible shape, it feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I've pampered this car like a member of the family, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, you've totally found it! I'd love for you to come take a look and see for yourself how gorgeous it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions at all!",
