    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This AP2-generation S2000 is a superlative example of Honda\u2019s high-revving engineering. Powered by the longitudinal F22C1 inline-four, the powerplant delivers linear power through a crisp six-speed close-ratio manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis remains factory-spec, featuring the rigid X-bone frame and double-wishbone suspension at all four corners, ensuring neutral handling and precise turn-in. All original VIN tags are intact, body panels show zero deflection, and the gearbox synchros operate with mechanical perfection. A truly unmolested, collector-quality roadster for the purist.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
