      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality specimen that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings, all protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the dashboard is crack-free, and the car retains its original factory scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is in peak condition, backed by a complete, chronological folder of every service record since its purchase. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen inclement weather. The sale includes both original master keys, the factory window sticker, and all original owner\u2019s manuals. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
